(126, 1, '2025-10-16 09:30:33', '2025-10-16 09:30:33', 'Nelly is a Doctor of Laws Candidate at the University of Pretoria. She holds a Master of Law (Pretoria) and a Bachelor of Laws (Kabarak). Nelly is an Advocate of the High Court of Kenya and a Certified Professional Mediator. Her research interest and areas of practice are digital trade, digital rights, and data protection and governance. Nelly currently heads the Data Policy and Governance and Cyber Law and Policy Departments.', 'Nelly C. Rotich', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nelly-c-rotich', '', '', '2025-10-16 09:30:33', '2025-10-16 09:30:33', '', 0, 'https://cipit.revamp.org.test/?post_type=team_member&#038;p=126', 0, 'team_member', '', 0),
