(148, 1, '2025-10-16 13:34:53', '2025-10-16 13:34:53', 'Professor and Researcher of Copyright and Public Policy at Graduation Program on Public Policy and Development the Federal University of Rio de Janeiro (PPED/UFRJ) and of Civil law, IP and Technology at the Law School at ITR/UFRRJ. PhD in Civil Law. Academic Visitor at Oxford University between (2017-2019). President of the Instituto Brasileiro de Direitos Autorais (IBDAutoral – Brazilian Copyright Institute). Researcher and vice-coordinator of the National Institute of Science ‘Proprietas’. Copyright Consultant at Fundação Oswaldo Cruz (FIOCRUZ) and at various national and international organizations. Member of the Copyright Committee of the BAR Association and of the Brazilian Intellectual Property Association.\r\n\r\n', 'Allan Rocha de Souza', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'allan-rocha-de-souza', '', '', '2025-10-16 13:34:53', '2025-10-16 13:34:53', '', 0, 'https://cipit.revamp.org.test/?post_type=steering_committee&#038;p=148', 0, 'steering_committee', '', 0),
