(150, 1, '2025-10-16 13:35:39', '2025-10-16 13:35:39', 'Cece Ojany Bekhor teaches leaders who value making an impact, how to BE well and DO well. She’s the Director and accredited Coach at TMP Coaching, a practice that is 11+ years old. Cece has worked with leaders of all genders, from diverse cultures & industries, both in Kenya and overseas. Her coaching style is entirely unique, putting humanity, creativity and effectiveness at the centre of the work. Together with 1:1 coaching, she also facilitates workshops, online and face-to-face for diverse organisations including CIPIT, The World Resources Institute, Stanford Seed, AHL Venture Partners, Zipline, The European Union, PULA to name a few. She’s also a published author. Her memoir “I’ll take some self love with that” is a book that particularly resonates with leaders living, working or who have teams in the global south.', 'Cece Ojany Bekhor', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cece-ojany-bekhor', '', '', '2025-10-16 13:35:39', '2025-10-16 13:35:39', '', 0, 'https://cipit.revamp.org.test/?post_type=steering_committee&#038;p=150', 0, 'steering_committee', '', 0),
